Title : Pego do Inferno
Text : '''Pego do Inferno''' is a small waterfall and lake located in the parish of [[Santo Estêvão]], in [[Tavira Municipality|Tavira]] in the [[Algarve]], [[Portugal]]. It is one of the three waterfalls formed by Asseca stream.{{Infobox waterfall
